CI/CD Overview

CI - Continuous Integration  <---- operates arround build process
CD - Continuous Delivery/Deployment <---- operates arround deployment process

CICD Pipeline = CI Pipeline + CD Pipeline

Sample CI Pipeline

Checkout Code into a VM ------> Unit Tests -----> Static Code Analysis ------> Build Artifact -------> Create the docker Image -------> Scan the Image -------> Push the Image to the Registry ------> Update the kubenetes manifest file
                                                                                                                                               
Sample CD Pipeline

Pull the Image from the Registry -------> Deploy the Image to the Dev Environment 


